Class MPDSong

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bff.javampd.MPDItem
      • org.bff.javampd.song.MPDSong
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<MPDItem>
    public class MPDSong
extends MPDItem
    MPDSong represents a song in the MPD database that can be inserted into a playlist.

    1.0
